# Cannot create Recipients

## Description


While trying to create a recipient from the form <b>Profiles and Target -- Recipients</b> on the instance, you may be getting rights to access the folder errors.


## Resolution


User was trying to create a recipient from the form <b>Profiles and Target -- Recipients</b> on his instance, but he was getting rights to access the folder errors as shown below:-

![](data:image/png;base64,)



<u><b>Issue Identified:-</b></u>

Customer had by mistake made the default folder Recipients as a view, which is wrong as the customer should have created a separate view folder for it.



<u><b>How the Issue was fixed:-</b></u>

Once we added the Recipient folder by right clicking on the folder form "Profiles and Target" , things started to work again.
